//-各區域的MIXIN 分別可以直接設定類別名稱，連結檔案位址，圖片位置，快搜敘述
mixin areablock(classname, areaposition, imgposition, altdiscription)
    div(class="" + classname + "")
        a(href="" + areaposition + "")
            img(src="" + imgposition + "", alt="" + altdiscription + "")




